get an anndata reference to 5k10k protein after totalVI from tutorial

Source: R/cache_citeseq_pbmcs.R
getPro5k10kAdata.Rd

get an anndata reference to 5k10k protein after totalVI from tutorial

getPro5k10kAdata()

Value

python reference to anndata

Note

It may be advantageous to set `options(timeout=3600)` or to allow an even greater time for internet downloads, if working at a relatively slow network connection.

Examples

getPro5k10kAdata()
#> AnnData object with n_obs × n_vars = 10849 × 14
#>     obs: 'n_genes', 'percent_mito', 'n_counts', 'batch', '_scvi_labels', '_scvi_batch', 'leiden_totalVI', 'CD3_fore_prob', 'CD4_fore_prob', 'CD8a_fore_prob', 'CD14_fore_prob', 'CD15_fore_prob', 'CD16_fore_prob', 'CD56_fore_prob', 'CD19_fore_prob', 'CD25_fore_prob', 'CD45RA_fore_prob', 'CD45RO_fore_prob', 'PD-1_fore_prob', 'TIGIT_fore_prob', 'CD127_fore_prob'
#>     var: 'protein_names'
#>     uns: 'dendrogram_leiden_totalVI', 'log1p'
#>     obsm: 'X_totalVI', 'X_umap'
